text.tspan: O Lord, You died for our sins.
By Your blood we’re cleansed from within.
All of our failures have now been washed away.
Conquer our death and our sin. Bring us to life.
Give us ears to hear what You say.
O Lord, from everything else we turn away.
O Lord, our eyes are on You.
Fill our hearts and minds with the truth.
O Lord, our whole life to You we consecrate.
